You can use number&amp;1 to confirm the first bit is 1 or 0, and use &gt;&gt; to shift each bit to the first.

    public static List&lt;Boolean&gt; convertIntToBooleanList(int i) {
        List&lt;Boolean&gt; list = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();
        list.add((i&gt;&gt;2&amp;1)!=0);
